    "day": 5,
    "title": "Kaya's Party Dress",
    "sentences": [
      "Kaya was excited for her friend's party.",
      "She looked at the calendar for the date.",
      "Kaya chose her favorite blue dress.",
      "She was always careful with her clothes.",
      "But then, some red jam dropped on her dress!",
      "\"Oh no!\" she said. It made an ink-like spot.",
      "She tried to clean it, but it was not well.",
      "Kaya quickly ran to the store to buy a new dress.",
      "The trouble was over soon.",
      "She did not need to go to the hospital."
    ]
  }
